Attribution
-----------

The `autoresearch` skill is inspired by Andrej Karpathy's `autoresearch`
project:

https://github.com/karpathy/autoresearch

The inspiration is methodological: bounded autonomous experiment loops,
metric-first evaluation, single-file scoped edits, baseline comparison,
and keep-or-discard candidate handling. No upstream source code is copied
into this repository.

The `bluegrid-xhs-illustrations` skill's structure and visual-system
approach were inspired by Ian's 小黑 illustration skill:

https://github.com/helloianneo/ian-xiaohei-illustrations

The inspiration is architectural and methodological: reusable IP character,
style DNA, composition patterns, prompt templates, QA rules, and example
assets. 小蓝格 is an independent personal IP adapted for Xiaohongshu-style
4:5 content and blue, clean creator-system visuals.

No Ian 小黑 source images, example assets, or prompt text are copied into this
repository.
